"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"This is one of the questions I often review because it helps me to conceive ideas in a longer time frame. I\\nI bet that users will flood into the encryption field in the next ten years, which will bring about a major change in the way users interact with technology.\\nFor example, in a meta-universe/social network, people have a public address that contains all NFT/art/digital land/flex items; a private address that can be easily used as a savings account, using stable currencies such as USDC/UST Generate income; a private address for DEX transactions/other transactions. All of these are connected through an undifferentiated user experience, where people can send messages to each other. this\\nIn one aspect, the questions worth thinking about are:\\nHow to create a seamless experience that includes social networks/banks/games in one place?\\nWhat platform can it be built on?\\nHow will this application be promoted to new users and millions of people? (Via) Gamification? (pass through)\\nNFT?\",\"timestamp\":1636196381,\"title\":\"What will become the killer app of the 2020s?\"},\"digest\":\"0lNkLozSO0VVePwUw0pnIdpW4Xz1WIl6YhFzYsGRPDs\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x48134B7c635d5D40fFF8E5EcE5417BA393975474\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"cIHfMdGrYKiNoktsJNliM5-GBtNEf7Svki77I4LBbhU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Kx4SeL8mMMSJrNc3kvhfsVNIKlNfqpVfA3MPjIRqWWo\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"3e5awz3v9yJ2eZYEFQww4vdvZzu9SvMvE10ZGjUc0WMoacXLPipyqxkc4OWaakfI2B2VQGGVPIt65eMXCI-1lg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x86559c2c50d110ca8a4c3db7539a0c79cea0a3e67172101cea52e61dc6c741a433d2deb429c3b7184d8615be5ae2ef27741af41bf0ba92d19f8b1420763f63d41b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"cIHfMdGrYKiNoktsJNliM5-GBtNEf